nhttps://www.loc.gov/events/\n</url>\n<query>\nLive! At the Library schedule\n</query>\n<result>\nLive! At The Library – Thursday\u202fOctober\u202f9\u202f2025\u202f5:00\u202fpm\u202f–\u202f8:00\u202fpm\u202fEDT  \nLocation: Thomas Jefferson Building, Great Hall  \nDescription: The Library’s Thomas Jefferson Building and all exhibitions will be open for extended hours on Thursdays. Visitors are invited to enjoy happy‑hour drinks and food available for purchase in the Great Hall and the Jefferson Building’s beautiful architecture while immersing themselves in the Library’s exhibits, collections and programs.  \n\nLive! At the Library: U.S. Poet Laureate Inaugural Event – Thursday\u202fOctober\u202f9\u202f2025\u202f7:00\u202fpm\u202f–\u202f8:00\u202fpm\u202fEDT  \nLocation: Thomas Jefferson Building, Coolidge Auditorium (LJ‑G45A)  \nDescription: Award‑winning poet Arthur\u202fSze will give his inaugural reading as the 25th Poet Laureate Consultant in Poetry at the Library of Congress. The historic reading marks the beginning of Sze’s laureateship; a book signing will follow. (Streaming information will be available closer to the event date.)\n</result>', include_extracted_content_only_once=True, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='<url>\nhttps://www.loc.gov/events/\n</url>\n<query>\nLive! At the Library\n</query>\n<result>\nLive! At The Library – Thursday\u202fOctober\u202f9,\u202f2025  \n- **Time:** 5:00\u202fpm\u202f–\u202f8:00\u202fpm\u202fEDT  \n- **Location:** Thomas Jefferson Building, Great Hall  \n- **Description:** The Thomas Jefferson Building and all exhibitions will be open for extended hours. Visitors can enjoy happy‑hour drinks and food (available for purchase in the Great Hall) while exploring the Library’s exhibits, collections, and programs.  \n\nLive! At the Library: U.S. Poet Laureate Inaugural Event Celebrating Arthur\u202fSze – Thursday\u202fOctober\u202f9,\u202f2025  \n- **Time:** 7:00\u202fpm\u202f–\u202f8:00\u202fpm\u202fEDT  \n- **Location:** Thomas Jefferson Building, Coolidge Auditorium (LJ‑G45A)  \n- **Description:** Poet Arthur\u202fSze will give his inaugural reading as the 25th Poet Laureate Consultant in Poetry at the Library of Congress, marking the start of his laureateship. A book signing will follow. Streaming information will be available closer to the event date.\n</result>', extracted_content='<url>\nhttps://www.loc.gov/events/\n</url>\n<query>\nLive! At the Library\n</query>\n<result>\nLive! At The Library – Thursday\u202fOctober\u202f9,\u202f2025  \n- **Time:** 5:00\u202fpm\u202f–\u202f8:00\u202fpm\u202fEDT  \n- **Location:** Thomas Jefferson Building, Great Hall  \n- **Description:** The Thomas Jefferson Building and all exhibitions will be open for extended hours. Visitors can enjoy happy‑hour drinks and food (available for purchase in the Great Hall) while exploring the Library’s exhibits, collections, and programs.  \n\nLive! At the Library: U.S. Poet Laureate Inaugural Event Celebrating Arthur\u202fSze – Thursday\u202fOctober\u202f9,\u202f2025  \n- **Time:** 7:00\u202fpm\u202f–\u202f8:00\u202fpm\u202fEDT  \n- **Location:** Thomas Jefferson Building, Coolidge Auditorium (LJ‑G45A)  \n- **Description:** Poet Arthur\u202fSze will give his inaugural reading as the 25th Poet Laureate Consultant in Poetry at the Library of Congress, marking the start of his laureateship. A book signing will follow. Streaming information will be available closer to the event date.\n</result>', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=True, success=True, error=None, attachments=[], long_term_memory='Task completed: True - Live! At the Library is scheduled weekly on **Thursdays** from **5:00\u202fpm to 8:00\u202fpm EDT** (the progr - 100 more characters', extracted_content='Live! At the Library is scheduled weekly on **Thursdays** from **5:00\u202fpm to 